#: index.php:364
msgid ""
"Rufus is a utility that helps format and create bootable USB flash drives, "
"such as USB keys/pendrives, memory sticks, etc."
msgstr ""
"Mae Rufus yn gyfleustodau sy'n helpu i fformatio a chreu gyriannau fflach "
"USB bootable, fel allweddi / pendrives USB, ffyn cof, ac ati."

#: index.php:365
msgid "It can be especially useful for cases where:"
msgstr "Gall fod yn arbennig o ddefnyddiol mewn achosion lle:"

#: index.php:367
msgid ""
"you need to create USB installation media from bootable ISOs (Windows, "
"Linux, UEFI, etc.)"
msgstr ""
"mae angen i chi greu cyfryngau gosod USB o ISOau bootable (Windows, Linux, "
"UEFI, ac ati)"

#: index.php:368
msgid "you need to work on a system that doesn't have an OS installed"
msgstr "mae angen i chi weithio ar system nad oes ganddo OS wedi'i osod"

#: index.php:369
msgid "you need to flash a BIOS or other firmware from DOS"
msgstr "mae angen i chi fflachio BIOS neu gadarnwedd arall o DOS"

#: index.php:370
msgid "you want to run a low-level utility"
msgstr "rydych chi am redeg cyfleustodau lefel isel"

#: index.php:372
msgid "Despite its small size, Rufus provides everything you need!"
msgstr ""
"Er gwaethaf ei faint bach, mae Rufus yn darparu popeth sydd ei angen arnoch "
"chi!"

#: index.php:373
msgid ""
"A non exhaustive list of Rufus supported ISOs is also provided at the bottom"
" of this page."
msgstr ""
"Mae rhestr nad yw'n gynhwysfawr o ISOau a gefnogir gan Rufus hefyd ar waelod"
" y dudalen hon."

