#: index.php:433
msgid ""
"I will take this opportunity to express my gratitude to the translators who "
"made it possible for Rufus, as well as this webpage, to be translated in "
"various languages. If you find that you can use Rufus in your own language, "
"you should really thank them!"
msgstr ""
"Cymeraf y cyfle hwn i fynegi fy niolch i'r cyfieithwyr a wnaeth yn bosibl i "
"Rufus, yn ogystal â'r dudalen we hon, gael ei gyfieithu mewn amryw o "
"ieithoedd. Os gwelwch y gallwch ddefnyddio Rufus yn eich iaith eich hun, "
"dylech chi wir ddiolch iddyn nhw!"

#: index.php:434
msgid "Usage"
msgstr "Defnydd"

#: index.php:435
msgid ""
"Download the executable and run it &ndash; no installation is necessary."
msgstr "Dadlwythwch y gweithredadwy a'i redeg &ndash; nid oes angen gosod."

#: index.php:436
msgid "The executable is digitally signed and the signature should state:"
msgstr "Mae'r gweithredadwy wedi'i lofnodi'n ddigidol a dylai'r llofnod nodi:"

#: index.php:438
