"To provide feedback, report a bug or request an enhancement, please use the "
"GitHub <a target=\"_blank\" %s>issue tracker</a>. Or you can <a "
"target=\"_blank\" %s>send an e-mail</a>."
msgstr ""
"I ddarparu adborth, riportio nam neu ofyn am welliant, defnyddiwch y traciwr"
" mater GitHub <a target=\"_blank\" %s>traciwr mater</a>. Neu gallwch <a "
"target=\"_blank\" %s>anfon e-bost</a>."

